quran[16]{c,v,t}:
  2,44,"Mbela on njamirat yimЙ“e Й—iggere njejjiton ko'e mon tawa oЙ—on njanga deftere nde, mbela on kakkilantaa Й—um"
  2,45,"Mballitoree muГұal e juulde, pellet honde saЙ—tani dow mbo yankiniiЙ“e Й“e"
  2,46,ЖҒeen yananaaЙ“e maa kawru e joom maЙ“Й“e ko he Makko Й“e nduttotoo
  2,47,"Onon Й“iЙ“Й“e Isra'iil ciftoree neemaaji Am Й—i neemin MI mon, ko Miin tigi Й“urni e dow winndre he"
  2,48,Kulee Гұande fittaandu alaa ko waawani fittandu wonndu ndu jaЙ“antaake tefangol goЙ—Й—o coodtiigu kadi jaЙ“etaake Й“e keЙ“ataa ballo
  2,49,"Tuma Min ndanndii on yimЙ“e Fir'awna Й“e mbaЙ—ii on lette bonЙ—e Й“e kirsa Й“iЙ“Й“e mon Й“e ngoppa rewЙ“e mon nguura, ina e Й—uum lette mawЙ—e iwde ga Jooma mon"
  2,50,Nde Min peccani on maayo ngo Min ndanndi on Min njooli yimЙ“e Fir'awna oЙ—on ndaarda gite mon ЕӢaas
  2,51,Nde Min podani Muusaa jammaaji capanЙ—e nayi fawii heen ndew-Й—on ngaari ndi caggal Am onon ko on tooГұooЙ“e
  2,52,Fawii heen Min ngaccani on Й“aawo Й—uum mbela joo njetton
  2,53,Nde Min ngaddani Muusa deftere nde e Furgaana mbela joo peewon
  2,54,Nde Muusaa wi'i yimЙ“e makko onon yimЙ“e am on tooГұii ko'e mon nde ndew-Й—on ngaari ndi nduttoЙ—ee e tagЙ—o on o mbarto-Й—on Й—uum Й“uri moЖҙЖҙande on to Jooma mon O accana on Kanko woni gaccanoowo njurmotooЙ—o
  2,55,Nde mbii-Й—on Muusaa min ngoonЙ—itaa haa min nji'a Alla ko laaЙ“i ndeen hartaango (jayngol iwde asamaan) Й“ami on oЙ—on ndaarda gite mon
  2,56,Fawii heen Min nguurtini on Й“aawo nde maay-Й—on mbela joo njetton
  2,57,"Min Й—uwdini on duule Min njippinani on njuumri dakmundi e colli juЙ—aaЙ—i Гұaamee e belЙ—i ko Min njeЙ—i on, wonaa Minen Й“e tooГұi ko ko'e maЙ“Й“e Й“e tooГұatnoo"
  2,58,Min mbii naatee ndee saare Гұaamon heen ko mbela-Й—on mbeltoron naatee damal ngal oЙ—on njankinii mbi'on accan min ndeen Min njaafoo on goopi mon Min Й“eydana moЖҙЖҙinЙ“e Й“ee moЖҙЖҙereeji
  2,59,TooГұЙ“e Й“ee mbayliti konngol ngol Й“e mbi'anoo ndeen Min njippini dow tooГұooЙ“e Й“ee lette sabu ko Й“e ngonno ko faasqeebe